## Automatic License Conversion

After the 3-year grace period from each version's release date, that specific version automatically converts to GPL (GNU General Public License v3.0). Each version is licensed independently based on its release date as specified in the version configuration.

**Example:**
- Version "0.9.0" (released 07-26-2025) → GPL on 07-26-2028
- Version "1.0.0" (released 2026-03-20) → GPL on 2029-03-20
- Version "1.1.0" (released 2027-07-10) → GPL on 2030-07-10

